%N A394728 Expansion of e.g.f. exp( sqrt(1-x^2) - 1 + x*arcsin(x) ) (even powers only).
%F A394728 a(0) = 1; a(n) = Sum_{k=1..n} binomial(2*n-1,2*k-1) * A001818(k-1) * a(n-k).
%F A394728 E.g.f. A(x) satisfies A'(x)/A(x) = arcsin(x).
%e A394728 E.g.f.: 1 + x^2/2! + 4*x^4/4! + 39*x^6/6! + 827*x^8/8! + 34380*x^10/10! + ...
